代码如下：
:'''<nowiki><div style="height:10em; overflow:auto; border: 2px solid #088">
ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ</div></nowiki>'''

